{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, just to prove to Leib if he ever listens to it-- he's probably dead-- to tell him that I did make it, that I learn a little bit, that I was not that naive, because he thought that I would be just eliminated in no time.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He looked at me like a little kid who-- you know, who just cannot survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe he was right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, what I did, for example, they used to bring you in a line, put you in a line and march you round, round, round.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if somebody in front would look at you, I would pick a terribly looking fellow, very tall, and stand behind him, because as they say, go, go, go, go, they'll pick him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'll go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, just to give you another flavor of what the situation of a selection would look like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the selections when I was selected, I was still in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He asked me what religion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no religious life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing religious about the whole place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was nobody-- I never saw anybody there religious or being involved in a religion.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I remember one event, which was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The day when I was selected to be eliminated in the hospital and the French physician was trying to remove me from the list-- or the young people that he wanted to remove, not only myself.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how many he removed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In a fact, after they came with the trucks, everybody who remained was very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] emotionally-- you know, survived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Look, I was just facing death and I'm here.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
